pr_body:
These refactoring changes are necessary for the React Native SDK.
Other changes that are needed for the SDK and could be handled in this MR:

-  Substituting ReactInstanceHandler with e.g. Broadcasting in ConnectionService.java
-  Refactoring of DropboxModule.java
-  Making BuildConfig not null when in React Native in AppInfoModule.java
